description: Nova Leap Health Corp. provides home and home health care services in the United States and Canada. Its services include dementia care, companionship, personal and respite care, cooking and meal preparation, bathing, dressing, grooming, housekeeping, errands, transportation, and medication reminders by nursing staff. Nova Leap Health Corp. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Halifax, Canada.
ceo: Mr. Christopher Donald Dobbin C.A., CPA, CA, CPA
